mdElement.text: Preconditions: - goods claimed must have been traded on the local market within the last 20 years. - No overdue payments for previous services rendered.

Quality requirements: - Scaleability: must be able to perform 400 valuations per month. - Performance: Valuations should be completed within 3 business days from receipt of request. - Reliability: The failure rate should be below 0.01%.
